   WELCOME
   Welcome to Le Tigre,
   a destination, a tribe,
   an ethos…

   Le Tigre welcomes you to all of its locations seven days a week, ready
   to take care of you, listen and understand how to best achieve your
   well-being, right from our very first encounter.

   Our mission is lived out every day, no matter your expectations,
   knowledge or level of practice, guiding you through the urban jungle
   towards gentle mind and body practices that matches your physical,
   emotional and energetic state in that given moment.


