   SPIRIT
   THE LE TIGRE ETHOS

   Le Tigre is, above all, a state of mind and a spirit of being. Le Tigre
   is a tribe of men and women who share a healthy, soothing, happy and
   aesthetic way of living. Le Tigre is a melting pot of attributes from
   across all horizons and all backgrounds, brimming with attentive,
   patient and generous talents. Le Tigre offers a path upon which
   everyone can advance at their own pace in connection with their body,
   spirit and breath, enabling them to discover their true being.
   FIND OUT MORE >
